[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/9378679.stm "Blackpool fined £25,000 by Premier League"] - BBC Sport, 27 January 2011</ref> Holloway was made aware of the fine over the phone while playing [[golf|golf]] with his wife at Shoreditch Golf Club in [[Chorley|Chorley]].<ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/ian-holloway-they-said-charlie-was-on-his-way-to-anfield-but-he-was-sat-next-to-me-in-my-office-2205697.html "Ian Holloway: They said Charlie was on his way to Anfield... but he was sat next to me in my office"] - ''The Independent on Sunday'', 6 February 2011</ref> He offered his resignation to Karl Oyston, but it was rejected.<ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/holloway-offers-resignation-after-premier-league-fines-blackpool-2197682.html "Holloway offers resignation after Premier League fines Blackpool"] - ''The Independent'', 29 January 2011</ref>

